{"type": "article", "id": 16397, "title": "诊所要清新宜人也不难：做好采光，多用木质，就像这样", "description": "明亮整洁，让医生和病人都有一个好心情", "date": "2015-10-21T16:00:00Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 12055, "name": "医院设计"}, {"id": 17582, "name": "公共设计"}, {"id": 17583, "name": "L. McComber ltée"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 4, "praise_count": 116, "image": "img/article/article_show/201607021229591UTIwruZj8pLElyO.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t位于加拿大魁北克市拉瓦尔地区的皮肤科诊所占据着一个商业楼中的一层，它原本是一家昏暗且令人压抑的儿童医院。为了让这里重新明亮起来，他们请来了建筑事务所 L.\r\nMcComber ltée 帮助改建。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span>L. McComber ltée 从房间规划入手，将原本靠窗的房间拆掉并移到中间，以便留出一条靠窗的走廊。光线通过走廊传到这层楼更深入的地方，不再如以往一样是一个黑暗的内部走廊。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122951NSbRGyuJdBlI0ngt.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"640\" title=\" 改造前\" alt=\" 改造前\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> 改造前</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122952duvGzybNY8gqQPCx.jpg\" width=\"650\" height=\"541\" title=\"改造前平面图\" alt=\"改造前平面图\" data-ratio=\"0.83230769\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>改造前平面图</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122952YsdWQ768EwB2HKou.jpg\" width=\"800\" height=\"641\" title=\"改造后平面图\" alt=\"改造后平面图\" data-ratio=\"0.80125\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>改造后平面图</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t6 个房间连成一排，前后都有木门，两边门同时打开，光线就能穿透进屋内了。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122952gDO4xml8UyhJKk15.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"640\" title=\"靠窗走廊\" alt=\"靠窗走廊\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>靠窗走廊</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122953DbnOuHKASzX8QmLR.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"641\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66770833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122953dgSK1QfjiaW4N0hn.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"640\" title=\" 诊断室内部\" alt=\" 诊断室内部\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> 诊断室内部</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t此外，房间靠近天花板处也空出了一段距离，<span>使用了乳白色的半透明的磨砂玻璃，使光线能投射进来并发射到其他地方。</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这层楼的中间规划了四间带弧形的房间，也用<span>磨砂玻璃环绕，很特别。</span>四个 U 型弧度组成了前台的墙面，让空间变得活泼。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122954SpVlBKWkwGT0x7JI.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"640\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t诊所的标志“D”挂在上面，U 型房间与标志“D”也是呼应的。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122954PR6pvg2SrIbNMoLq.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"640\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t木材部分统一使用白蜡木，清爽自然。木质天花板上内置了白色的灯，让这块离自然光最远的地方也能保持明亮。通透的视线和自然材料搭配，令人感到信任和舒服。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<span></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607261437003LiWfonAdN0FwZzO.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"640\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" style=\"text-align:center;\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122955mXWR9Ke0hzIO5gN3.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"640\" title=\"前台\" alt=\"前台\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>前台</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span style=\"text-align:justify;\"></span><img src=\"img/uploads/20160726143701jMmplb0HOYifEtsg.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"728\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.67407407\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122955DJbnXCsvIZ0aNF48.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"640\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122956hcBzbNCZms0rW9Ie.jpg\" width=\"960\" height=\"641\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66770833\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122956aGTRXw7zNmfn4c6M.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"652\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.6037037\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122957mVYXngxDu8FrOHsf.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"721\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.66759259\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160702122957pGuHnBq2TWy0NOkP.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"720\" title=\"休息室\" alt=\"休息室\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>休息室</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201607021229580ZqN426PKakvBdfu.jpg\" width=\"1080\" height=\"720\" title=\"等候区\" alt=\"等候区\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>等候区</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:left;\">\r\n\t<span>图片来自<a href=\"http://www.gooood.hk/clinique-d-diaphane-by-l-mccomber-ltee.htm\" target=\"_blank\"> gooood</a>、<a href=\"http://lmccomber.ca/\" target=\"_blank\">lmccomber</a></span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}